Vibe-Trading — HKUDS — MIT License
https://github.com/HKUDS/Vibe-Trading
  The pre-trade safety design in `bitarena/firewall/` (an immutable
  bounded-autonomy mandate, a fail-closed pre-trade gate, and the
  halt / daily-count / universe / notional / exposure / leverage checks) is a
  clean reimplementation inspired by Vibe-Trading's live order-guard and mandate
  model. The optional "swarm" competitor agent can wrap Vibe-Trading when it is
  installed in the environment.

FinRL — AI4Finance Foundation — MIT License
https://github.com/AI4Finance-Foundation/FinRL
  Available (optionally, via the `[rl]` extra) as a heavier RL competitor; the default
  RL agent is an original, dependency-free tabular Q-learner.

